{"title":"数字黑洞","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3042","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>随手写出一个三位数，（要求三位数字不能全部相同），按照数字从大到小的顺序，把三位数字重新排列，得到一个新数，。接下来，再把所得的数的数字顺序颠倒一下，又得到一个新数。把这两个新数的差作为一个新的三位数，再重复上述的步骤。例如：332</p>\n<p>332-233=099（注意：这里可以以0开头）</p>\n<p>990-099=891</p>\n<p>981-189=792</p>\n<p>972-279=693</p>\n<p>963-369=594</p>\n<p>954-459=495</p>\n<p>所有的三位数最后都会陷入495这个黑洞里再也出不来了。。。。。。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>给你一个三位数N</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>打印出到495的步骤</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>303</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>330-033=297</p>\n<p>972-279=693</p>\n<p>963-369=594</p>\n<p>954-459=495</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>这无需提示和数据范围了吧</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}